# Architecture Notes

## Workflow Goal
This workflow performs AI-assisted KYC/OSINT screening for an individual or organization and generates a reviewer-oriented report for human decision support.

## Main Layers
- Intake
- Validation
- AI Search Planning
- Search Collection
- Findings Normalization
- Findings Analysis
- Reporting
- Final Webhook Response

## AI Usage
Two Gemini-powered AI agents are used:
1. Search Planner Agent
2. Findings Analyst Agent

## Search Provider
Web search is executed using Serper.

## Reporting
The workflow creates:
- structured JSON output
- a Word-report mapping object
- a Google Doc report

## Human Review Principle
The workflow does not make the final compliance decision. Final judgment remains with a human analyst.
